    {
      "id": "edge-class-proof-overview",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Edge Class Proof",
      "position": {
        "x": -100,
        "y": -180
      },
      "width": 540,
      "height": 220,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Edge Class Proof\n\nThis graph puts canonical edge-class references on real edge instances.\n\nWhat it proves now:\n\n- edge instances carry `edgeClassRef` as semantic authority\n- `edgeClassKey` remains available as compatibility/search metadata\n- one edge uses an instance-level render override\n\nUse the class ports below and the edge inspector together.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
