    {
      "id": "edge-class-proof-inspect-note",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "How To Inspect",
      "position": {
        "x": 520,
        "y": -180
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 220,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# How To Inspect\n\n1. Select a sample edge.\n2. Look for `data.edgeClassRef` first, then `data.edgeClassKey`.\n3. Compare the reference to the class artifact linked below.\n\nThe orange dependency edge also carries an instance-level stroke override. That is intentional: classes provide defaults; instances may override.",
        "_classBinding": {
